snippet.title: New Image of Bruised Amber Heard Emerge: I Truly Feared For My Life
snippet.description: Shocking new details in the domestic violence allegations against Johnny Depp by his estranged wife have emerged. Dramatic photos inside the latest issue of People magazine show Amber Heard with a bruised eye and cut lip. Heard claims Depp has been abusing her for years and tells the magazine: "There was one severe incident in December 2015 when I truly feared for my life." An unnamed friend of Heard claimed to the New York Post that the 52-year-old actor once tried to suffocate [Heard] with a pillow. #InsideEdition
